name: SaaSMAX
overview:
SaaSMAX, Inc. provides an online marketplace that electronically facilitates the reselling and purchasing of Software-as-a-Service business applications (SaaS Apps) through value-added resellers, solution providers, trusted advisors and other reseller channels. (collectively Solution Providers).

The SaaSMAX App Marketplace enables: 1. SaaS software vendors to display detailed marketing and technical information, commission plans, special incentive offers, and the ability to manage and track reseller commissions; and, 2. Solution Providers to identify relevant SaaS Apps for their clients, receive compensation when they facilitate the sale of a SaaS App, and track and manage their customers purchases. The SaaSMAX App Marketplace will provide SaaS software vendors and Solution Providers with the tools and relationships to increase their revenues in the rapidly growing $12+ Billion SaaS industry.
